event_description: Cobra Man is a Los Angeles Power Disco band led by members Andy Harry and Sarah Rayne. The band is known for their 7 piece high energy spectacle shows and their collaboration with Worble skate collective.

Fresh off their long-awaited full-length collaboration "The Elephant Man’s Bones" Roc Marciano and The Alchemist are heading over to Europe to present their brand new album! RRC MUSIC CO. in collaboration with Skatecafe are proud to present the first show of this run here in Amsterdam on Thursday October 27th! The event, which also represents Roc Marciano's first ever live appearance in Europe, will start at 7.30PM with Wyclef  warming up the crowd, the two legendary rapper-producers will be rocking the stage at 9PM, and we're closing the night with Duo Penossi, who earlier in the day will be hosting a pop-up at their iconic Platypus Recordshop location at Zeedijk 45, look out for more informations about that real soon! This will be one for the books!

De Nacht van de Hete Bliksem: vechten, feest, verbroedering en ontlading.
Op 15 oktober toont Boogieland [Kick]Boxing Club zich wederom als bokstempel meets nachtclub, ditmaal samen met de vrienden van het Skatecafé.

Boogieland’s Nacht van de Hete Bliksem is een viering van de menselijke potentie tot overwinning; een knetterend spektakel ter algehele verrukking en een liefdevolle verstoring van de gevestigde orde.

Hét boksgala / festival dat Boogieland zo’n unieke identiteit geeft en waar alles waar wij van houden samenkomt. Deze nacht draait om vechten en feesten zonder machoshit, doordrenkt van punkmentaliteit en mét hoogenergetische waanzin overal om je heen.
